channel.title: Problems with making 525 webclient
channel.description:
OK well the subject doesnt tell the whole story. The whole story is: I got a source and a client..... I got a jar maker and made the client..... The problems: As I have seen in the other tuts for 525 they tell me to look in class73 to take out a code for the window frame.... yet I have nothing in it about that or (if im messed up on details) the so called "client ip" is supposed to be in it which it isnt. I have checked most other places for ip and nothing comes up. Although I have changed the ip in 2 other docs were it is correct but when I compile it seems to work because I have no errors but it still will not work Also, it tells me in the tut to put my manifest as client2 which I do not have in either my source or my client folder.
If you any other details if I missed please tell me and I will add Thank you for your time OH and tell me if in wrong section, I will gladly move it
